  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nTime flies, devcon4 passed, and the beacon chain spec grew up including some significant changes, e.g., `CrystallizedState` and `ActiveState` were combined into `BeaconState`. It makes more sense to rework the data structures before we move forward to implement logic, e.g., rework helper functions, `BeaconStateMachine`, and `BeaconChain`.\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n1. Disable most `tests/beacon` tests.\r\n2. Rework the `eth/beacon/types` as [spec](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/blob/master/specs/core/0_beacon-chain.md#data-structures) described.\r\n",
